Posts.Content: That certainly is worrisome isn't it? Until Tuesday comes, try to do some things that will take your mind off of it for awhile. I know easy for me to say. Get your fears out with a friend, spouse. It could be nothing, or it could be something. What ever the outcome, you will do what ever has to be done. We are all a heck of a lot stronger than we think we are, and I'm sure you are too. Hang in there! God Bless.
Posts.Title: Lump Under Right Clavicle!
